 :actor/purpose   "L4 Care Tier — multi-generational nurturing. Childcare (infants through early childhood) + eldercare + continuity-of-care pathways. 5 Pregel cells with privacy-first, structurally encrypted care sessions. Cross-actor sibling: mitate (diagnostic routing). Constitutional gates enforce consent, caregiver vetting, human-in-loop, emergency escalation, and multi-generational ratio balance."
